{"tid":822651,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【山竹遠去】六間大學宣布　學生及教職員明天毋須回校 (20:08)","createTime":"2018-09-16T12:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T12:47:11.000Z","uid":125113,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7841a9bdedd37c8f74b45a5fa21e7f858fb123a9","tid":822651,"uid":125113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T12:23:05.000Z","msg":"香港科技大學宣布，由於強颱風「山竹」襲港，於各區造成破壞，考慮多個交通管道受影響，大學亦有設施需要清理及維修，為確保學生及員工安全，決定明天（17日）無論是否仍有熱帶氣旋警告或暴雨警告生效，科大學生及教職員均無須回校。<br />\n<br />\n香港教育大學、浸會大學、中文大學、城市大學和理工大學均有類似安排。各校宣布，除緊急維修工作人員或必須回校當值的職員，所有教職員和學生均毋須返回校園。<br />\n<br />\n本報正向其他大專院校了解明日上課安排。<br />\n<br />\n教育局已在較早時候宣布，考慮到社區各項設施需時清理和維修，為確保學生安全，明天（17日）所有中小學均停課。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c3f45cef6e0c585dd0919d8d2d9833ee919096","tid":822651,"uid":45914,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T12:24:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e124aee002a1156fecb8106999079a7998fe7d3","tid":822651,"uid":66253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T12:25:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"16161dd17d348c9509f29ef195d609549dccb078","tid":822651,"uid":18479,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T12:25:21.000Z","msg":"恒大係college 係咪同中學生睇齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32133493abd2c224348b46007bf4a7bb24fefcac","tid":822651,"uid":88443,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T12:25:30.000Z","msg":"HKU <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c657b9a16e604806104bf61e4a6db29119fcd9fc","tid":822651,"uid":198998,"like":3,"dislike":0,"scor